    <bug_when>2016-07-03 22:25:33 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>Created attachment 1175756
Patch to fix the problem of determination of NLSClass

This proposed patch determines whether a character is a control code at the first in NLSClassify().  Function NLSClassify() never returns NLSCLASS_NL, NLSCLASS_TAB and NLSCLASS_CTRL when drawPrompt flag is true unless this patch is applied.</thetext>
